To compile:

   mpicc -o hello.exe hello.c

   
   OPTIONS:

   -o specifies the filename of the executable



To run:
 
   mpiexec -np 4 -f nodes.txt ./hello.exe


   OPTIONS:

   -np specifies the number of processes/tasks
   -f  specifies the filename containing the hostnames of the nodes 


For more info contact jachermocilla@gmail.com
